title: Threats to abortion access drive demand for abortion pills, analysis suggests
description: Requests for abortion pills from people who were not yet pregnant spiked when patients appeared to perceive threats to abortion access, new research has found.

title: Russia strikes residences and a supermarket in Ukraine's capital and other cities
description: Russia launched dozens of attack drones and missiles — including its advanced Kinzhal hypersonic missile — according to Ukrainian officials.

title: Up First briefing: Israel Supreme Court ruling; South Korean opposition leader stabbed
description: Israel's Supreme Court rejects right-wing changes to the judiciary. South Korea's Democratic Party leader Lee Jae-myung was stabbed in the neck during a visit to the city of Busan.

title: Powerful earthquakes along Japan's western coast leave multiple people dead
description: Aftershocks continued to shake Ishikawa prefecture and nearby areas on Tuesday, a day after a magnitude 7.6 temblor slammed the region on Monday afternoon.
